prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon watercolor of a slightly frazzled, very fluffy gray cat attempting to balance a precarious stack of colorful, lopsided birthday gifts. One paw is outstretched for balance, and it has a wide-eyed, comical expression of intense concentration. A single, tiny party hat is slipping off its head. In the center, written in a beautiful, readable, and elegant handwritten cursive script, is the text "happy birthday". The entire scene is a flat 2D artwork in a watercolor painting style, featuring soft flowing colors, visible artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds at the edges of the figures. The background is a simple, clean off-white with light pastel watercolor washes.
